{"id": "webh_gallery", "modality": "web", "name": "Gallery", "task": {"description": "Build an image gallery page 'Shots' at 1920px wide. A header with the title and a filter bar of 5 category pills (All active, Nature, Urban, People, Abstract). Below, a masonry-style grid of at least 12 image-placeholder cards arranged in 4 columns; cards have varying heights but the COLUMNS stay equal width with uniform gutters and the cards pack without large ragged gaps. Each card has a hover-caption bar with a title and a small heart/like count. A 'Load more' button is centered at the bottom. Responsive: at 375px the grid becomes a single column and the filter pills become a horizontally scrollable row.", "requirements": ["A filter bar shows five category pills with 'All' active", "The grid arranges at least 12 cards in 4 equal-width columns with uniform gutters", "Card heights may vary (masonry) but the four columns remain equal width and aligned", "Cards pack without large ragged vertical gaps between columns", "Each card has a caption bar with a title and a like count, not clipped", "A centered 'Load more' button appears below the grid", "Filter pills share one consistent style with the active pill visually distinct", "On desktop nothing overflows horizontally", "At 375px the grid becomes a single column and the filter pills scroll horizontally in their own row", "Image placeholders maintain consistent styling/spacing (repetition)"], "difficulty": "hard"}, "runs": [{"run": 1, "ss_n_defects": 118, "ss_text_overlap": null, "ss_clipped": null, "ss_overflow": null, "ss_total_tokens": 6971, "rv_n_defects": 2, "rv_text_overlap": null, "rv_clipped": null, "rv_overflow": null, "rv_iterations": 3, "rv_total_tokens": 36360}, {"run": 2, "ss_n_defects": 118, "ss_text_overlap": null, "ss_clipped": null, "ss_overflow": null, "ss_total_tokens": 7148, "rv_n_defects": 56, "rv_text_overlap": null, "rv_clipped": null, "rv_overflow": null, "rv_iterations": 3, "rv_total_tokens": 37937}, {"run": 3, "ss_n_defects": 118, "ss_text_overlap": null, "ss_clipped": null, "ss_overflow": null, "ss_total_tokens": 7148, "rv_n_defects": 50, "rv_text_overlap": null, "rv_clipped": null, "rv_overflow": null, "rv_iterations": 3, "rv_total_tokens": 37570}], "ss_img": "images/web/webh_gallery_ss.jpg", "rv_img": "images/web/webh_gallery_rv.jpg", "ss_html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Shots - Image Gallery</title>\n    <style>\n        * {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            background-color: #fafafa;\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            max-width: 1920px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 0 40px;\n        }\n\n        /* Header */\n        .header {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);\n            color: white;\n            padding: 60px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 60px;\n        }\n\n        .header h1 {\n            font-size: 4rem;\n            font-weight: 700;\n            letter-spacing: -2px;\n            margin-bottom: 16px;\n        }\n\n        .header p {\n            font-size: 1.25rem;\n            opacity: 0.9;\n            font-weight: 300;\n        }\n\n        /* Filter Bar */\n        .filter-bar {\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            gap: 16px;\n            margin-bottom: 60px;\n            padding: 0 20px;\n        }\n\n        .filter-pill {\n            background: white;\n            border: 2px solid #e0e0e0;\n            border-radius: 50px;\n            padding: 12px 24px;\n            font-size: 1rem;\n            font-weight: 500;\n            color: #666;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: all 0.3s ease;\n            white-space: nowrap;\n        }\n\n        .filter-pill.active {\n            background: #667eea;\n            border-color: #667eea;\n            color: white;\n            transform: translateY(-2px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.3);\n        }\n\n        .filter-pill:hover:not(.active) {\n            border-color: #667eea;\n            color: #667eea;\n            transform: translateY(-1px);\n        }\n\n        /* Masonry Grid */\n        .gallery {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);\n            gap: 24px;\n            margin-bottom: 80px;\n        }\n\n        .gallery-item {\n            background: white;\n            border-radius: 16px;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);\n            transition: all 0.3s ease;\n            position: relative;\n            cursor: pointer;\n        }\n\n        .gallery-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-8px);\n            box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);\n        }\n\n        .image-placeholder {\n            width: 100%;\n            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #f0f0f0, #e8e8e8);\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: center;\n            color: #999;\n            font-size: 1.1rem;\n            font-weight: 500;\n            position: relative;\n        }\n\n        /* Varying heights for masonry effect */\n        .gallery-item:nth-child(1) .image-placeholder { height: 280px; }\n        .gallery-item:nth-child(2) .image-placeholder { height: 320px; }\n        .gallery-item:nth-child(3) .image-placeholder { height: 240px; }\n        .gallery-item:nth-child(4) .image-placeholder { height: 360px; }\n        .gallery-item:nth-child(5) .image-placeholder { height: 300px; }\n        .gallery-item:nth-child(6) .image-placeholder { height: 260px; }\n        .gallery-item:nth-child(7) .image-placeholder { height: 340px; }\n        .gallery-item:nth-child(8) .image-placeholder { height: 280px; }\n        .gallery-item:nth-child(9) .image-placeholder { height: 320px; }\n        .gallery-item:nth-child(10) .image-placeholder { height: 240px; }\n        .gallery-item:nth-child(11) .image-placeholder { height: 300px; }\n        .gallery-item:nth-child(12) .image-placeholder { height: 360px; }\n        .gallery-item:nth-child(13) .image-placeholder { height: 280px; }\n        .gallery-item:nth-child(14) .image-placeholder { height: 320px; }\n        .gallery-item:nth-child(15) .image-placeholder { height: 260px; }\n\n        .caption-overlay {\n            position: absolute;\n            bottom: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            right: 0;\n            background: linear-gradient(transparent, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8));\n            color: white;\n            padding: 24px 20px 20px;\n            transform: translateY(100%);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .gallery-item:hover .caption-overlay {\n            transform: translateY(0);\n        }\n\n        .caption-title {\n            font-size: 1.1rem;\n            font-weight: 600;\n            margin-bottom: 8px;\n        }\n\n        .caption-likes {\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            gap: 6px;\n            font-size: 0.9rem;\n            opacity: 0.9;\n        }\n\n        .heart-icon {\n            width: 16px;\n            height: 16px;\n            fill: #ff6b6b;\n        }\n\n        /* Load More Button */\n        .load-more-container {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 80px;\n        }\n\n        .load-more-btn {\n            background: #667eea;\n            color: white;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 50px;\n            padding: 16px 40px;\n            font-size: 1.1rem;\n            font-weight: 600;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: all 0.3s ease;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.3);\n        }\n\n        .load-more-btn:hover {\n            background: #5a67d8;\n            transform: translateY(-2px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.4);\n        }\n\n        /* Mobile Responsive */\n        @media (max-width: 375px) {\n            .container {\n                padding: 0 20px;\n            }\n\n            .header {\n                padding: 40px 0;\n                margin-bottom: 40px;\n            }\n\n            .header h1 {\n                font-size: 2.5rem;\n                letter-spacing: -1px;\n            }\n\n            .header p {\n                font-size: 1.1rem;\n            }\n\n            .filter-bar {\n                overflow-x: auto;\n                justify-content: flex-start;\n                padding: 0 20px;\n                margin-bottom: 40px;\n                scrollbar-width: none;\n                -ms-overflow-style: none;\n            }\n\n            .filter-bar::-webkit-scrollbar {\n                display: none;\n            }\n\n            .filter-pill {\n                flex-shrink: 0;\n                padding: 10px 20px;\n                font-size: 0.9rem;\n            }\n\n            .gallery {\n                grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n                gap: 20px;\n                margin-bottom: 60px;\n            }\n\n            .gallery-item:nth-child(n) .image-placeholder {\n                height: 280px;\n            }\n\n            .load-more-container {\n                margin-bottom: 60px;\n            }\n\n            .load-more-btn {\n                padding: 14px 32px;\n                font-size: 1rem;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header class=\"header\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>Shots</h1>\n            <p>Discover amazing photography from talented creators</p>\n        </div>\n    </h